Body: Description: Hi there, one of our users cannot access USB on his computer. He is in the right security group and everything looks fine from our AD side and his permission within Endpoint Protector. Do you know what could be going wrong or where I can look?
What We've Learned Updated: Provided steps and new client version to the customer.
Next Steps Updated: Waiting for customer to confirm a remote session.
Next Steps Updated: The meeting is set for Monday 2PM RO time.
